{"guid":"123456789","username":"twitter.YarnStudioGames","content":"/* ---[ EMBEDED VERSION ] ---*/

/* STORY DETAILS */

@story is called "Julia's three good rocks",
    has id "threeGoodRocks-v1",
    is described as
    "Julie has found three good rocks, but which of them is the best rock?".

/* THE HERO */

#You
    is an @actor,
    is named "Julia",
    is in #TheBackyard.

/* THE PLACES */

#TheBackyard:
    is a #Room,
    is called "The Backyard",
    has scenery
    "http://hgtvhome.sndimg.com/content/dam/images/hgtv/fullset/2013/7/12/1/BPF_original_double-swing-set-transitional_beauty_shot-2_h.jpg.rend.hgtvcom.1280.960.jpeg",
    is described as "Julia's backyard is small but it's ok, because Julia is also very small.
    The grass is full of pretty yellow dandelions and the sandbox has been well dried by the mornind sun.
    It's a beautifull day",
    has in it a #SwingSet.

/* OBJECTS */

#SwingSet:
    is a #thing,
    is called "Swing Set",
    has image
    "http://hgtvhome.sndimg.com/content/dam/images/hgtv/fullset/2013/7/12/1/BPF_original_double-swing-set-transitional_beauty_shot-2_h.jpg.rend.hgtvcom.1280.960.jpeg",
    is described as "The metal poles of the two seat swing set are gleaming from their new coat of bright red paint.".

#TheSandbox:
    is a #room,
    is called "My Favorite Sandbox",
    is described as "The small meter wide sandbox is turtle shaped and green...
    like green turtles. Julia loves turtles. She sure wished she had a turtle.".

#TheBackyard links to #TheSandbox.
#TheSandbox links to #TheBackyard.
